<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
  <title>Fuzic &bull; Maintenance</title>
  <style>
    article {
      width: 25em;
      border-radius: 1em;
      padding: 1em;
      background: #E82C0C;
      color: #FFF;
      margin: 10% auto 0;
      font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px #888;
    }
    
    h1 {
      padding: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #FFF;
      margin: 0 0 1em 0;
    }
    
    p {
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    p:last-child {
      margin-top: 0.5em;
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    a {
      color: inherit;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <article>
    <h1>Fuzic closed for maintenance</h1>
    <p>Fuzic is not available currently as its database is being upgraded. This is estimated to take a few hours (starting 7PM UTC). Sorry for the inconvenience - it will be back shortly.</p>
    <p><a href="http://www.twitter.com/fuzicnl">@fuzicnl</a></p>
  </article>
</body>